caption.text:
LUMii BRIGHT 100 W LED Fixture
LUMii BRIGHT is a 100 W full spectrum white light LED fixture, ideal as both an independent or a supplementary lighting source. Each fixture is comprised of two linked LED boards with a specially designed internal driver.

The LUMii BRIGHT fixture is ideal for reducing heat in your growing environment and runs much cooler than other lighting sources.

The modular fixture allows you to connect multiple fixtures in series (up to 6) to suit a variety of growing needs, such as growth and flowering stages, supplemental lighting, dark corners in your grow room, maintaining donor plants and boosting yields. 
Find your local stockist at - http://www.grow-lumii.com/

LUMii BRIGHT is a 100 W full spectrum white light LED fixture, ideal as both an independent or a supplementary lighting source. Each fixture is comprised of two linked LED boards with a specially designed internal driver.

The LUMii BRIGHT fixture is ideal for reducing heat in your growing environment and runs much cooler than other lighting sources.

The modular fixture allows you to connect multiple fixtures in series (up to 6) to suit a variety of growing needs, such as growth and flowering stages, supplemental lighting, dark corners in your grow room, maintaining donor plants and boosting yields. 
Find your local stockist at - http://www.grow-lumii.com/

caption.text:
LUMii BRIGHT 100 W LED Fixture
LUMii BRIGHT is a 100 W full spectrum white light LED fixture, ideal as both an independent or a supplementary lighting source. Each fixture is comprised of two linked LED boards with a specially designed internal driver.

The LUMii BRIGHT fixture is ideal for reducing heat in your growing environment and runs much cooler than other lighting sources.

The modular fixture allows you to connect multiple fixtures in series (up to 6) to suit a variety of growing needs, such as growth and flowering stages, supplemental lighting, dark corners in your grow room, maintaining donor plants and boosting yields. 
Find your local stockist at - http://www.grow-lumii.com/
